// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3126 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c41c91a0-3d3a-5212-abfe-23e788aef3bf

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
